android.content.ComponentCallbacks
public class NetmeraIntentService
extends android.app.IntentService

This class is responsible to listen notifications and handle communications between services.In order to send push notification the following XML must be added between the <application></application> tags in the AndroidManifest.xml file.

<service android:name="com.netmera.mobile.NetmeraIntentService"/>

getPushId

public static java.lang.String getPushId()
Get Netmera push notification ID of the incoming push. If the notification is rich, you can use NetmeraPushService.handleRichPushWithId(android.webkit.WebView, String) method by using the ID as parameter to handle the notification.

push id
